listing_company_name: The Realest Estate - PASCOE VALE SOUTH
description:
If you’ve been searching for that perfect block of land to build your dream family home, then 8 Storkbill View in Harkness is a must-see.

The 1132sqm, slightly-elevated grassy block is nestled down the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, within a family friendly neighbourhood. Whether you’re looking to build a large family home with a swimming pool and entertaining area (STCA), or a smaller home with beautifully landscaped gardens, this great property is sure to impress.

Adding further to the appeal is the location of the land. Local playgrounds and bus stops are a short walk away, and a short drive will have you at the Woodgrove Shopping Centre, as well as a great selection of local schools, cafes and amenities. The centre of Melton is a 6-minute drive away and access to major roads is within easy reach, connecting you to the Melbourne CBD in under an hour and the airport in 30-minutes.
